record.Name: Zoom Video Communications
record.Description: Zoom Video Communications is a software-based conference room solution used for video conferences around the world. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in San Jose, California.

record.Name: ZoomInfo
record.Description: ZoomInfo was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Washington. The company offers a business-to-business data platform utilized by sales and marketing teams, recruiters, and other business professionals for lead generation and detailed information on people and companies.
